<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Economist</TITLE></HEAD>
<img src="econlogosmall.gif" alt="The Economist Logo"></td>
<td align=center valign=top>
</HEAD>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<BODY>
<ul>
<H1>The weekly journal of ideas and analysis</H1>





<P>

<I>The Economist</I> is a weekly news and opinion newspaper offering

reporting, commentary and analysis on world politics, global business,

finance and economics, science and technology and the arts.

<P>

Founded in 1843 to support the cause of free trade, the newspaper

has remained true to its mission ever since. Today, <I>The Economist</I>

is firmly established as one of the world's most influential and

authoritative publications.

<P>

The editorial staff of <I>The Economist</I> enjoy a unique independence from outside financial control: the constitution of The Economist Newspaper Ltd does not permit any individual or organisation to gain a majority shareholding. <I>The Economist</I> also differs from all other major news and opinion publications in the anonymity of its contributors. These factors guarantee <I>The Economist</I> a truly independent single voice.

<P>

With a circulation in excess of 600,000, <I>The Economist</I>

is read by opinion-formers in more than 180 countries around the

world.
<HR>
</ul>


<P>

<br><p align=center>
<a href="index.html"><i>The Economist</i> Home Page</a>





