http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/15-02-97/ir6149.html 199.173.162.110 19970215011209 text/html 6333
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 01:08:07 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 13-Feb-97 19:31:05 GMT
