HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 01:27:30 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 25-Oct-96 10:59:07 GMT
Content-length: 4745
Content-type: text/html
