</DOCHDR>
<html><head><title>A survey of international banking</title></head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<table width=100%><tr><td align=left valign=top><!img src="../images/ibsu.gif"  alt="Sp Survey">
<td align=right valign=top><img src="http://www.economist.com/econlogosmall.gif" width=78 height=39  alt="The Economist"></td></tr></table>

