<DOCNO>WT09-B15-157</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA096-001029-B004-277</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/08-02-97/br7730.html 199.173.162.110 19970215014309 text/html 5724
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 01:39:06 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 06-Feb-97 21:31:04 GMT
