http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/01-02-97/fn6559.html 199.173.162.110 19970215014923 text/html 3362
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 01:45:10 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 30-Jan-97 19:05:34 GMT
