<DOCOLDNO>IA096-001030-B009-379</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/18-01-97/sf0814.html 199.173.162.110 19970215015413 text/html 19196
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 01:50:09 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 16-Jan-97 18:11:29 GMT
