<DOCHDR>
http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/18-01-97/am3192.html 199.173.162.110 19970215015425 text/html 9426
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 01:50:18 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 16-Jan-97 18:11:28 GMT
Content-length: 9239
