http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/11-01-97/ld4503.html 199.173.162.110 19970215015718 text/html 7424
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 01:53:14 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 10-Jan-97 12:23:33 GMT
